          <td id="LC206" class="blob-code blob-code-inner js-file-line"><span class="pl-kos">&lt;</span><span class="pl-ent">p</span><span class="pl-kos">&gt;</span>This is an R Markdown document, created for the Coursera course &amp;ldquo;Reproducible Research&amp;rdquo;, in completion of &amp;ldquo;Peer Assessment 1&amp;rdquo;.
